See http://aqla.net

Contrubutions are welcome!

Build requirements:
Windows
Sandcastle
.NET 4

Put to /deployscript:
UnityEngine.dll (find in Unity editor directory)
UnityEditor.dll (find in Unity editor directory)
ILMerge.exe (download from microsoft website)
zip.exe (console zip archiver)


Make build:
run /deployscript/!DeployFull.bat
open in unity "JustLogicBuildTest"
export asset


Merging all units to core JustLogic.dll library is required for backward compatibility.
